info.author: Dave Brown
classifiers: License :: Free To Use But Restricted
info.description:
PyNIO is a Python package that allows read and/or write access to a variety of
scientific data formats 
using an interface modelled on netCDF.
info.keywords: netCDF, GRIB, HDF, scientific data formats
info.name: PyNIO
info.platform:
MacOSX (Intel and PPC)
32-bit and 64-bit (x86_64) Linux
SGI/IRIX64
Solaris 9
